Brooks Benedict https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brooks_Benedict 0 Brooks Benedict (born Harold J. Mann, February 6, 1896 – January 1, 1968) was an American actor of the silent and sound film era, where he played supporting and utility roles in over 300 films, mostly uncredited.
